{"tid":686281,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Republic HC 08537 IPO","createTime":"2018-06-01T06:15:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T16:45:35.000Z","uid":66701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"3b97cdce0800fae12339a70f9646b7b38ce526ba","tid":686281,"uid":66701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T06:15:08.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】新加坡基本健康護理服務提供者Republic Healthcare(08357)公布在港上市計劃，發售1.3億股，10%公開發售，90%配售，集資最多7800萬元。每股招股價0.5元至0.6元，一手5000股，入場費3030.23元。<br />\n<br />\n該公司集資所得約28.5%用作策略性地拓展及鞏固以「Dr. Tan &amp; Partners」品牌經營的全科醫療診治中心；約15.7%用作增設新「S Aesthetics」品牌經營的醫學美容診治中心；約46.9%用作吸納及挽留醫生及員工人才；約6.4%用作提升改善訊息科技基礎設施與系統；約1.1%作設立中央藥庫；約1.4%作一般營運資金。<br />\n<br />\n股份今日起至下周三(6日)招股，6月15日在創業板掛牌，獨家保薦人天泰金融服務。（nc）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似幾正咁<br />\nSingapore 醫HIV <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c565fdc85eb7b684050063dcde0556951f8c1288","tid":686281,"uid":66701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T08:25:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3547b57a5d0dfd48b114c2bb895a1a66e35595c","tid":686281,"uid":31923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T08:33:15.000Z","msg":"有啲野收埋食算啦，越多散戶知越大機會仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"436624bafe18c6b3eaf8783d6c999af7d3514e9a","tid":686281,"uid":66701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T08:35:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 收到"},{"pid":"4b05a5c4fdd2743a8867075ea7e04f2bf0dafeb3","tid":686281,"uid":29781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:26:02.000Z","msg":"有冇人抽"},{"pid":"f7a9ea18c47b44b370cfcb84a817a6fe4f594df7","tid":686281,"uid":66701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTi